\v 29 Moses said, “I am going to go out from you and pray to the \nd Lord\nd*, and the swarms of flies will go away from Pharaoh, from his servants, and from his people tomorrow. Only do not let Pharaoh deal falsely again by not releasing the people to sacrifice to the \nd Lord\nd*.”
